# Obsidian Smart Capture (OSC)

## Purpose
OSC is a stateless AI-powered capture pipeline that transforms
raw notes into Obsidian-native atomic Markdown files.

## Philosophy
Capture fast.
Structure slow (via AI).
Store nothing.

## Architecture
User (PWA)
→ API Gateway
→ AWS Lambda
→ OpenAI GPT-4o
→ GitHub Repo
→ Obsidian Vault

## Key Properties
- Stateless
- Deterministic output
- Zero vendor lock-in (Markdown + Git)
- PKM-first design (Zettelkasten, Atomic Notes)

## AI Behavior
- No memory
- Strict system prompt
- Tag whitelist
- YAML guaranteed valid
